subject: GOOD DAY TO YOU THIS MORNING
body:
GOOD DAY TO YOU THIS MORNING.
THE TRUTH WILL ALWAYS SET YOU FREE AND PLEASE TELL ME WHY YOU ARE TELLING ME A LIE?
YOUR'S TRULY
BARRISTER DEAN WESTWOOD

subject: Re:   GOOD DAY TO YOU THIS MORNING
body:
Hello Barrister Dean Westwood,

Good day to you too! I hope this message finds you well. I'm not sure what you're referring to when you mention a lie. Could you please elaborate on that? I'm always open to discussions and clarifications.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
James
